title: Darius maining be like...
body:
*Does good* : "Omg Darius daddy ur god plz carry our bronze butts"
*Does bad*: "You are literally the worst darius I've ever seen. Imagine losing as a darius lol"
*asks for a gank*: "You dont need a gank, youre darius"
*Comments how the matchup is bad for me and I will most likely lose the lane*: "Lol ur just bad"
*Brings all of the enemy toplane to let my botlane get ahead and get drags*: "Darius stop overextending"

:C
